welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Fort Lewis, a charming city known for its rich history and stunning natural landscapes. We invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that our beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both military and civilian flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at McChord AFB Airport handles all freight and military transport flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but a valid military ID is required to access the network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport handles all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport is used for shipping and receiving goods.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for Alaska Airlines flights.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights and some domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bremerton Airport serves all commercial flights and provides a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Bremerton Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a more personalized experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal of Sanderson Field Airport, handling all commercial and private flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
